import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './LoginAndRegister.css'; const LoginAndRegister = () => { const [showLogin, setShowLogin] = useState(true); return (
{showLogin ? (
Don't have an account? setShowLogin(false)}>Sign Up
Login

Have an account? setShowLogin(true)}>Login
Sign Up
